review_blob: Had this on draft at the pub and took home a growler and was very impressed (~4.2), but I just had it cask-conditioned and it blew me away. So much more creamy off the cask with a solid, luscious head. Sweeter and fuller with better mouthfeel than the version carbonated off the tap head. Get the cask-conditioned version while you can!
beer_name: Tired Hands We Are All Infinite Energy Vibrating at the Same Frequency
